data.chText: 母亲已逐渐衰弱到无法独居。
data.enText: Mother was becoming too frail to live alone.
the frail stems of the flowers

simple_means.memory_skill: frail 脆弱的 → fract → 易碎的 → 脆弱的

ex.chText: 她母亲长期患病，身体很虚弱。
ex.enText: Her mother was weak from a long illness.

ex.chText: 在戒烟问题上我意志很薄弱。
ex.enText: I'm very weak when it comes to giving up smoking.

ex.chText: 敌人力量变弱，无法再继续这场战争了。
ex.enText: The enemy became so weak that they could not go on with the war.

synonyms.bx: 最普通用词，使用范围很广，既可指身体虚弱无力的，也可引申用于力量、意志、权力、性格等方面，表示“薄弱的”、“软弱的”等。

ex.chText: 他的脉搏太弱了，摸不着。
ex.enText: His pulse was too feeble to feel.
The newborn baby gave a feeble cry.

ex.chText: 她那虚弱的胳臂无力地垂在身边。
ex.enText: Her feeble arm dropped powerless to her side.

synonyms.bx: 语气较 weak 强，尤指身体、脉搏、声音等极为虚弱而无力的。

ex.enText: The old man is growing thin and frail.

ex.chText: 她仍然感觉身体有点虚弱。
ex.enText: She was still feeling a bit frail.

ex.chText: 她虚弱的手几乎连杯子也拿不住。
ex.enText: Her frail hands could hardly hold a cup.

synonyms.bx: 多指因年迈或生病而身体瘦弱的、虚弱的、衰弱的。

tr: a basket for holding dried fruit (especially raisins or figs)
the weight of a frail (basket) full of raisins or figs
easily broken or damaged or destroyed
example: a kite too delicate to fly safely

tr: wanting in moral strength, courage, or will
having the attributes of man as opposed to e.g. divine beings

value.def: Someone who is frail is not very strong or healthy.

example.ex: She lay in bed looking particularly frail.
example.tran: 她躺在床上，看上去特别虚弱。

value.def: Something that is frail is easily broken or damaged.

example.ex: The frail craft rocked as he clambered in.
example.tran: 他爬进来的时候，那件易碎的工艺品摇晃起来。

rootsaffixes.indicate: = to break, to shatter 打碎；破碎
rootsaffixes.title: fract, frag

partsOfSpeech.dec: dif 分开 + fract 打碎；破碎 → 分成碎片 → 分解
fract 打碎；破碎 + ion 表名词 → 碎片 → 部分
frac 打碎；破碎 + tion 表名词 + al …的 → 碎片的
fract 打碎；破碎 + ious …的 → 脾气易被击坏的 → 易怒的
fract 打碎；破碎 + ure 表状态 → 破碎的状态 → 断裂
frag 打碎；破碎 + ile 易…的 → 易碎的
frag 打碎；破碎 + ment 具体物 → 破碎的部分 → 碎片
frail 脆弱的 → fract → 易碎的 → 脆弱的
re 回 + fract 打碎；破碎 → 打碎〔光线〕→ 折射
re 相反 + fract 打碎；破碎 + ory …的 → 打不碎的 → 倔强的
